rows.label: tlk006101_07_msg0001
rows.name:
I never thought salvager training would
be so tough...

rows.label: tlk006101_07_msg0002
rows.name:
It's actually pretty scary... I feel like
I'm going to dread the diving part.

rows.label: tlk006101_07_msg0004
rows.name:
It's not like we have anywhere else to
go, and we promised to repay the
kindness everyone's shown us.

rows.label: tlk006101_07_msg0005
rows.name:
I'm still new to this, but I'll stick at it.
I'll be a first rate salvager someday,
just wait and see!
